DTEND;TZID=Europe/Paris:20260430T203000
SUMMARY:J5 · 🇬🇧 English emlyon — Self-presentation 5 min
DESCRIPTION:emlyon peut tester l'anglais. Commence maintenant.\n\nStructure self-presentation 5 min :\n→ (15 sec) "The WEF documents 92 million jobs displaced by 2030\, but 170 million created. Disruption hits entry-level jobs first."\n→ (30 sec) Pourquoi école de commerce : Kaufman's 5 functions + learning-by-doing\n→ (30 sec) Pourquoi emlyon : maker spirit + action from year 1 + "I don't want to study management — I want to practice it."\n→ (15 sec) Vision : "I see myself at the intersection of management and digital transformation."\n\n→ Enregistre → réécoute → refais 1 prise améliorée
CATEGORIES:ANGLAIS,EMLYON
END:VEVENT

