DESCRIPTION:ACTION 1 — Simulation express emlyon (20 min)\n→ Debout\, chrono\n→ Pitch 90 sec adapté emlyon (une seule fois)\n→ 2 questions difficiles à voix haute\n→ Dors avant 22h30. L'oral est à 14h.\n\nACTION 2 — Simulation anglais complète (40 min)\n→ ① Self-presentation 5 min en anglais (version emlyon)\n→ ② Thème : "AI\, automation and the future of work" (3 min)\n   FACT : "The WEF documents 92M jobs displaced\, 170M created by 2030."\n   MECHANISM : "Entry-level white-collar jobs are most at risk from agentic AI."\n   SCHOOL LINK : "That's why business schools that teach through real projects are more relevant than ever."\n→ ③ Vision 10 ans : "I see myself at the intersection of management and digital transformation. WEF identifies emotional intelligence\, foresight\, and authentic leadership as critical for 2030 — exactly what emlyon builds."\n\n→ Enregistre → réécoute demain dans le transport
